<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav ul {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
            list-style: none;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Content Section */
        .content {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        form input, form textarea {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        form input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
    display: flex; /* Use flexbox for centering */
    justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
    align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 40px;
    height: 60px; /* You can adjust the height as needed */
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/">{{name1}}</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Contact Us Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or concerns, we'd love to hear from you. Our team is here to assist you with all of your inquiries. Whether you're looking for more information about our services or need support with an existing booking, feel free to reach out using the contact form below or through any of our contact details.</p>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>Our Contact Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@yourservicecompany.com</p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +123 456 7890</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Service Road, Suite 456, Service City, Country</p>
        </div>

        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea placeholder="Your Message" rows="6" required></textarea>
            <input type="submit" value="Send Message">
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Service Company</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
